core values






Core Values




Safety - For employees and contractors, for local communities, for the environment.
Community - We value the contributions of our neighbors while also recognizing our responsibility to be active participants in local communities.
Communication - Open communication within the Company, with shareholders, and with local communities; open and transparent reporting; transfer of knowledge and expertise.
Teamwork - Sharing ideas, assets and talents.
Respect for People and Nature - Protecting the environment; care for individuals and the cultural integrity of communities.
Integrity - Guided by our Code of Ethics at every level of the Company.







